00:44:58,986 --> 00:45:00,066
You won't have that
with Lightning.


970
00:45:01,226 --> 00:45:02,866
Lightning connectors
just stop by the end


971
00:45:02,866 --> 00:45:03,856
and they start working.


972
00:45:05,236 --> 00:45:06,946
Another important
