997
00:46:19,406 --> 00:46:22,876
So, we definitely do recommend
that your accessories make use


998
00:46:22,976 --> 00:46:26,206
of the USB host mode
on Apple devices.


999
00:46:26,286 --> 00:46:27,956
And by this, I mean
just be clear


